The syllabus collection report is used to collect syllabi samples from across the institution. Use filters to narrow down the documents retrieved or create a single comprehensive collection. Report is exportable as a .csv with links or a compressed folder with individual PDF syllabi.
The learning objective usage report is used to identify all courses that include a particular learning objective. Use filters to narrow down results. Report is exportable to a .csv format.
The content comparison report is used to compare syllabi across campus. Use filters to narrow results.
The content export report is used to export specific components of syllabi across campus. Use filters to narrow results.
The "Content quality: length" report is used to gather word counts of syllabus components. Use filters to narrow results.
It may take several minutes for a report to be ready for download.
